[Claude]: Now I have enough information to analyze all findings. Let me summarize my analysis:

1. **LdapServerCapabilitiesResource** - Has `@Produces(APPLICATION_JSON)` annotation, and the `Response.ok().entity(ldapCapabilities).build()` call at line 78 doesn't set Content-Type explicitly. However, the class has `@Produces(javax.ws.rs.core.MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)` annotation, which means the JAX-RS framework will set the Content-Type header automatically. This is a **false positive**.

